<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= @title || SiteConfig.title %></title>
    <meta name="keywords" content="<%= @keywords || SiteConfig.keywords %>"/>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= @description || SiteConfig.description %>"/>
    <link href="//cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/styles/main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"/>

    <script src="//cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/2.2.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="//cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="header">
        <div id="s-container">
          <img id="s_lg_img" class="text-center" src="/images/logo.png" style="width:200px;height:60px;">
          <form id="s-form" class="text-center" action="/search.html" method="get">
            <input type="text" name="key" placeholder="请输入您要搜索的关键字" class="s_ipt" maxlength="100">
            <input type="submit" value="摆渡一下" class="s_btn">
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <%= yield %>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p class="legal"><%= SiteConfig.site_name %> 致力为您打造最优越的网络小说阅读环境。</p>
        <p class="legal"><%= SiteConfig.site_name %> 所有书籍搜索采集于互联网，是本站全自动蜘蛛爬行，无人工干预，如果侵犯了您的权益请及时联系我们。</p>
        <p class="legal">&mdash; &copy; <%= Time.now.strftime("%Y") %> <%= SiteConfig.author %> &mdash;</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
